import Home from './components/home/home'
import Login from './components/Login/login';
import Admin from './components/admin/admin';

const routes ={
    home: {
        type: "collapse",
        name: "Home",
        key: "home",
        route: "/home",
        component: <Home />,
        noCollapse: true,
        completed_sets: 0,
        total_sets: 0,
        sets: false,
        admin: false,
        icon: "homeIcon.png"
    },
    alphabet: {
        type: "collapse",
        name: "Alphabet",
        key: "alphabet",
        route: "/alphabet",
        component: <Home />,
        noCollapse: true,
        completed_sets: 0,
        total_sets: 1,
        sets: true,
        admin: false,
        icon: "alphIcon.PNG"
    },
    vocab: {
        type: "collapse",
        name: "Vocabulary",
        key: "vocab",
        route: "/vocab",
        component: <Home />,
        noCollapse: true,
        completed_sets: 0,
        total_sets: 10,
        sets: true,
        admin: false,
        icon: "wordIcon.png"
    },
    sent: {
        type: "collapse",
        name: "Sentences",
        key: "sent",
        route: "/sent",
        component: <Home />,
        noCollapse: true,
        completed_sets: 0,
        total_sets: 10,
        sets: true,
        admin: false,
        icon: "sentenceIcon.png"
    },
    tense: {
        type: "collapse",
        name: "Tenses",
        key: "tense",
        route: "/tense",
        component: <Home />,
        noCollapse: true,
        completed_sets: 0,
        total_sets: 10,
        sets: true,
        admin: false,
        icon: "tensesIcon.png"
    },
    read: {
        type: "collapse",
        name: "Reading",
        key: "read",
        route: "/read",
        component: <Home />,
        noCollapse: true,
        completed_sets: 0,
        total_sets: 10,
        sets: true,
        admin: false,
        icon: "readingIcon.png"
    },
    write: {
        type: "collapse",
        name: "Writing",
        key: "write",
        route: "/write",
        component: <Home />,
        noCollapse: true,
        completed_sets: 0,
        total_sets: 0,
        sets: false,
        admin: false,
        icon: "writingIcon.png"
    },
    preferences: {
        type: "collapse",
        name: "Preferences",
        key: "preferences",
        route: "/preferences",
        component: <Home />,
        noCollapse: true,
        completed_sets: 0,
        total_sets: 0,
        bottom: true,
        sets: false,
        admin: false,
        icon: "settingIcon.png"
    },
    admin: {
        type: "collapse",
        name: "Admin",
        key: "admin",
        route: "/admin",
        component: <Admin />,
        noCollapse: true,
        completed_sets: 0,
        total_sets: 0,
        bottom: true,
        sets: false,
        admin: true,
        icon: "adminIcon.png"
    }
};

export default routes;
